description._content: Catalog #: 09_01807 Title: Colonel L.C. Hurd Special Collection Photo Philippines Additional Information: Nine Us Army pilots standing in front of De Havilland DH-4 aircraft at Clark Field, the Philippines. Left to right - capt. Midcaf, Lt. Mebber, Lt. Lindgrove, Lt. Riby, Capt. Phillipe, Maj. Stefles, Lt. Johnson, Lt. Hurd and Lt. Liveley, Colonel L.C. Hurd served in the US Army Air Corps in the late 1920s and 1930s, Corporation Name: De Havilland Aircraft Company Tags: Colonel L.C.
